question: Which fast food restaurant can I find towards Northeastern University Silicon Valley, San Jose, CA within 170 kilometers from Golden Gate Bridge Lookout, Sausalito, CA?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.486003 37.82872)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-121.786342 37.257214)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.486003 37.82872)',4326)::geography, 170000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.486003 37.82872)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
